@url = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Check Server Health
GET {{url}}/

### 2. Register New Account (IMPORTANT: Email required for password recovery test)
POST {{url}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "minhthang",
  "password": "minhthang123",
  "email": "admin@hotel.com", 
  "accountTypeID": 2
}

### 3. Login
POST {{url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "minhthang",
  "password": "minhthang123"
}

### 4. Forgot Password (Use the email registered in step 2)
POST {{url}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@hotel.com"
}

### 5. Reset Password (Get OTP from Server Terminal and paste here)
POST {{url}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@hotel.com",
  "otp": "123456", 
  "newPassword": "newpassword999"
}